    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Content
</head>
      <p>Papers chiefly from the term of Albert G.A. Balz, a chairman of the Charlottesville School Board include files on committees, curriculum, enrollment, property, student promotion and graduation, and teachers.
</p>
